Ward {2}
Whenever this creature becomes the target of a spell or ability you control, put a +1/+1 counter on it.
Remove a +1/+1 counter from this creature: It gains your choice of vigilance, reach or trample until end of turn.

Vigilance, ward {1}
Each player can't cast more than one spell from their hand each turn.
Your opponents can't cast spells or activate abilities during your turn or combat.
